EA: 12C5104Desired Skills and ExperienceTo be eligible for this outstanding opportunity you will have at least 8 years of recruitment experience, with proven track record with an executive search firm. You should have the ability to manage P&L, great leadership & influencing skill and enjoy working in a team-driven, fast paced and entrepreneurial environment. About this companyMcCallEstablished in 1992, McCall is an award winning, market leading Recruitment to Recruitment consultancy with offices in the UK and Singapore. McCall attracts and places candidates at all levels from billing consultants & branch managers to senior executive/director/MD level across the staffing industry covering a wide wide of sectors from Accounting, Banking & Finance, FMCG & Supply Chain, Construction, Engineering & Technical including Oil & Gas Recruitment, Marketing & Media, Medical, Healthcare, Pharmaceutical & Life Sciences, I.T & Telco, Property, Retail & Sales Recruitment. Our clients range from large global organisations to local independent consultancies operating within either a Contingent or Search / Selection fashion. We have the expertise and knowledge to truly assist you in your career search, whatever the level.Similar jobsSingaporePosted 5 days agoSingaporePosted 6 days agoSingaporePosted 21 days agoSingaporePosted 41 days agoSingaporePosted 13 days agoSingaporePosted 12 days agoSingaporePosted 28 days agoSingaporePosted 1 day agoSingaporePosted 26 days agoSingaporePosted 27 days agoThis is a preview of the Recruitment Consulting Manager/ Consulting Director – Executive Search, Singapore job at McCall. To view the full job listing, join LinkedIn - its free!Join LinkedIn - its free!People also searchedPeople also viewedSingaporePosted 6 days agoSingaporePosted 12 hours agoSingaporePosted 15 days agoSingaporePosted 20 days agoSingaporePosted 19 days agoSingaporePosted 15 days agoSingaporePosted 15 days agoSingaporePosted 13 days agoSingaporePosted 16 days agoSingaporePosted 